  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SCORE — Multiplayer Football. One City. Endless Progression.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Score</strong> is an online multiplayer football experience inspired by the spirit of <strong>Multiplayer Soccer Clubs</strong>, rebuilt from the ground up for player progression, club rivalries, and a persistent shared world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete in full 11-vs-11 matches, build your dream club with friends, climb league divisions, qualify for international tournaments — and use your earnings to shape your life in a living multiplayer city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just football, progression, and a world built around the sport. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with passion. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get it all.</p>",
